      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/451655-i-rigoberta-mench-an-indian-woman-in-guatemala">Quotes from I, Rigoberta Menc...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
